ActNorthwest Territories Act
SubjectThorburn, Hon. Julie A. Northwest Territories Supreme Court
PrecisOrder appointing the Hon. JULIE A. THORBURN as a deputy judge of the Supreme Court of the Northwest Territories to hold office during good behaviour until attaining the age of seventy-five years.
